Class ShoppingCartSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • cop4331.model.ShoppingCartSystem

  • public class ShoppingCartSystem
extends java.lang.Object
    ShoppingCartSystem is a singleton class to make sure only single object gets created This class provides a way to access its only object which can be accessed directly without need to instantiate the object of the class.
